contentrichtext.text: '''Bricks''' may refer to: * [[Brick]], an artificial stone made by forming clay into rectangular blocks * [[Brick (electronics)]], a slang term for a device that cannot function due to internal failure(s) * [[BRICKS (software)]], an EC-funded, open-source software framework for digital libraries * [[Brick (song)]], a song by Ben Folds Five * [[Bricks (band)]], a late-1980's lo-fi alternative band fronted by [[Mac McCaughan]] of [[Superchunk]] * Bricks, a 1975 album by [[Hello People]] {{disambig}}
